cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

This paper is about a bidding optimization framework for e-commerce sponsored search, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for matching advertisements with search queries, machine learning (LG) for designing bidding strategies, artificial intelligence (AI) for building a customer intelligent agent, data structures (DS) for managing large-scale online experiments, and computer engineering (CE) for deploying the framework on a real-world platform. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, and cs.CE.
